  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced", 
    "date": "1984-05-10", 
    "text": "Environmental Crimes and Penalties Amendments of 1984 - Increases penalties (civil fines, criminal fines, and criminal sentences) for specified violations of the following Acts: (1) the Toxic Substances Control Act; (2) the Clean Air Act; (3) the Solid Waste Disposal Act (hazardous waste management provisions); and (4) the Comprehensive Environmental Response, Compensation, and Liability Act of 1980 (Superfund)."
